{
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "beach_1",
      "name": "Beach",
      "paragraphs": [
        "You wake up on the beach.",
        "The salty taste of the sea is notable.",
        "Your clothes are heavy and soaked."
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Stand up",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "beach_2"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "beach_2",
      "name": "Beach",
      "paragraphs": [
        "You rise up slowly and look around.",
        "You're not sure if you're stranded on an island or even a continent.",
        "But one thing is for certain. You have no idea where you are.",
        "Above the beach you spot some trees - or maybe a forest?"
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Walk up to the trees",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "beach_3"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "beach_3",
      "name": "Beach - Forest Entrance",
      "paragraphs": [
        "Indeed, there is a forest here.",
        {
          "text": "Just at the entrance there's a palm tree with a coconut.",
          "hideIfFlag": "have_opened_coconut"
        },
        {
          "text": "Just at the entrance there's a palm tree.",
          "showIfFlag": "have_opened_coconut",
          "ignoreSortByFlag": true
        },
        {
          "text": "If only you had something that could chop it down.",
          "showIfFlag": "have_food",
          "hideIfAnyFlag": ["have_sword", "chopped_down_palm_tree"]
        },
        {
          "text": "> You punch the palm tree. It really hurt. You're quite sure that you shouldn't do that again.",
          "showIfFlag": "punched_palm_tree"
        },
        {
          "text": "> Did you really punch the palm tree again? You start bleeding.",
          "showIfFlag": "punched_palm_tree_again"
        },
        {
          "text": "> You chop down the palm tree.",
          "showIfFlag": "chopped_down_palm_tree"
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Chop down palm tree",
          "showIfFlag": "have_sword",
          "hideIfFlag": "chopped_down_palm_tree",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "chopped_down_palm_tree"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Inspect felled palm tree",
          "showIfFlag": "chopped_down_palm_tree",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "beach_palm_tree"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Punch tree",
          "hideIfAnyFlag": ["punched_palm_tree", "chopped_down_palm_tree"],
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "punched_palm_tree"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Punch tree again",
          "showIfFlag": "punched_palm_tree",
          "hideIfAnyFlag": [
            "chopped_down_palm_tree",
            "punched_palm_tree_again"
          ],
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "punched_palm_tree_again"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Enter the forest",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "forest_1",
              "chapterId": "chapter_3"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "beach_palm_tree",
      "name": "Beach - Palm Tree",
      "paragraphs": [
        "The palm tree lays before you.",
        "You're certain you can open the coconut with your sword.",
        "But you're also convinced that your sword will break in the process.",
        {
          "text": "> Your sword breaks. But you now have an opened coconut. It smells juicy.",
          "showIfFlag": "have_opened_coconut"
        },
        {
          "text": "> You take the coconut. Maybe you will find something that can open it later?",
          "showIfFlag": "have_coconut"
        },
        {
          "text": "> You said a prayer to the fallen palm tree.",
          "showIfFlag": "prayed_for_palm_tree"
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Open coconut [sword will break]",
          "showIfFlags": "have_sword",
          "hideIfFlag": "have_opened_coconut",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "have_opened_coconut"
            },
            {
              "type": "remove_flag",
              "target": "have_sword"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Pray to the fallen palm tree",
          "hideIfFlag": "prayed_for_palm_tree",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "prayed_for_palm_tree"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go back to the Forest Entrance",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "beach_3"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
